                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120115-82-off481 t18120115-82-cd482"></join>, a pair of sheets, value 12 s. and a towel, value 1 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120115-82-victim851" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Trueman
